the third stage.

00:14:49.390 --> 00:14:52.690
The truth is sometimes
ridiculed, sometimes opposed,

00:14:52.690 --> 00:14:55.190
and rarely seen as self-evident.

00:14:55.190 --> 00:14:58.990
And this is why I
made "The Connection."

00:14:58.990 --> 00:15:00.480
This is a film
for people who are

00:15:00.480 --> 00:15:03.250
well and who want to stay well.

00:15:03.250 --> 00:15:06.450
This is a film for
people who are sick

00:15:06.450 --> 00:15:08.930
and who are searching
for answers.

00:15:08.930 --> 00:15:11.320
This is a film I wish my
doctor had have handed me

00:15:11.320 --> 00:15:13.460
when I first got sick.

00:15:13.460 --> 00:15:15.110
I hope that, after
