of realizing the truth.

00:15:20.850 --> 00:15:23.950
Or even better, that the
stages we travel through

00:15:23.950 --> 00:15:26.100
are more like those that
the philosopher William

00:15:26.100 --> 00:15:27.910
James proposed.

00:15:27.910 --> 00:15:30.820
"First, a new theory
is attacked as absurd.

00:15:30.820 --> 00:15:34.940
Then it is admitted to be true,
but obvious and insignificant.

00:15:34.940 --> 00:15:38.610
And finally, it is
seen to be so important

00:15:38.610 --> 00:15:42.360
that even its adversaries
claim that they themselves

00:15:42.360 --> 00:15:43.940
discovered it."

00:15:43.940 --> 00:15:48.472
