stress and there's

00:18:21.620 --> 00:18:25.280
bad stress, particularly
allostatic load,

00:18:25.280 --> 00:18:28.910
which is the chronic
overload of stress.

00:18:28.910 --> 00:18:31.920
And I know, from
my own experience,

00:18:31.920 --> 00:18:34.970
my autoimmune disease was
triggered by allostatic load.

00:18:34.970 --> 00:18:38.350
It had been constant stress.

00:18:38.350 --> 00:18:40.790
It was the constant deadlines
of being a journalist.

00:18:40.790 --> 00:18:43.480
But on top of that, I
was the sort of person

00:18:43.480 --> 00:18:46.010
who would take on the emotional
problems of other people

00:18:46.010 --> 00:18:47.500
that I couldn't fix.

00:18:47.500 --> 00:18:51.480
And that was contributing to
an emotional kind of stress

00:18:51.480 --> 00:18:52.600
in my body.

00:18:52.600 --> 00:18:56.270
And as Dr. Hassed talks
about in the film,

00:18:56.270 --> 00:18:57.950
there's this constant
wear and tear

00:18:57.950 --> 00:19:00.800
of the body, the constant
release of these stress

00:19:00.800 --> 00:19:03.780
chemicals, like cortisol.

00:19:03.780 --> 00:19:08.400
They slowly, slowly
start impacting your body

00:19:08.400 --> 00:19:10.220
in a detrimental way.

00:19:10.220 --> 00:19:12.270
Now, what's really
important to know

00:19:12.270 --> 00:19:15.680
is that we've evolved
to have the stress

00:19:15.680 --> 00:19:17.530
response as a good thing.

00:19:17.530 --> 00:19:19.050
It's supposed to save our lives.

00:19:19.050 --> 00:19:21.277
We're supposed to be able
to run away from the tiger

00:19:21.277 --> 00:19:23.110
that's chasing us, or
the elephant stampede,

00:19:23.110 --> 00:19:24.510
or whatever it is.

00:19:24.510 --> 00:19:26.220
It's supposed to
give us more energy,

00:19:26.220 --> 00:19:30.310
and it's supposed to allow our
blood to heal wounds faster.

00:19:30.310 --> 00:19:34.690
But when our body is constantly
activating this response,

00:19:34.690 --> 00:19:36.820
it's shutting down
other vital systems,

00:19:36.820 --> 00:19:40.940
like your digestion, which
means that it's not digesting

00:19:40.940 --> 00:19:45.902
nutrients in the
best possible way.

00:19:45.902 --> 00:19:47.610
The question that you
